3. Run the target stage's hat sequence for this unit only (do NOT re-run completed units)
4. Persist the updated output
5. Return to the current stage (${activeStage2}) -- this is a scoped side-trip
6. Commit: \`git add .haiku/intents/${slug}/stages/${targetStage}/ && git commit -m "refine: add output to ${targetStage} stage"\``;
          return {
